标题：床、褥子（bed, sleeping mat）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：יָצוּעַ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：yatsu‘a)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:4\">GEN 49:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr5:1\">1CH 5:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job17:13\">JOB 17:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps63:7\">PSA 63:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:3\">PSA 132:3</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מִטָּה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：mitah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen47:31\">GEN 47:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen48:2\">GEN 48:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:33\">GEN 49:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:28\">EXO 7:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:13\">1SA 19:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:15\">1SA 19:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:16\">1SA 19:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:23\">1SA 28:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam4:7\">2SA 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:19\">1KI 17:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:4\">1KI 21:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs1:4\">2KI 1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs1:6\">2KI 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs1:16\">2KI 1:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:10\">2KI 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:21\">2KI 4:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:32\">2KI 4:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs11:2\">2KI 11:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr22:11\">2CH 22:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:25\">2CH 24:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:6\">EST 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth7:8\">EST 7:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps6:7\">PSA 6:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:14\">PRO 26:14